'''kirehe''' ni akarere gaherereye mu burasirazuba bw'u [[Rwanda]] kakaba gahana imbibi na [[Akarere ka Ngoma|Ngoma]] , [[Akarere ka Kayonza|kayonza]],  [[Uburundi]] , [[Tanzaniya]] . 

[[Umugezi]] w'[[Akagera]] niwo uhuza akarere ka Kirehe n'igihugu cya Tanzaniya. Akarere ka Kirehe gatuwe n'abaturage bagera kuri 340,893 batuye ku buso bwa km 1,1188.5(ibarura rusange ry'abaturage rya 2012).<ref>{{Cite web |title=Archive copy |url=https://kirehe.gov.rw/index.php?id=83 |accessdate=2020-07-18 |archive-date=2020-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720010112/https://kirehe.gov.rw/index.php?id=83 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

